# Metadata Validator - Harita Hive Professional Tool
# MIT License
#
# Validates and auto-generates metadata for shapefiles, rasters, GeoJSON, etc.
# Ensures FGDC and ISO 19115 compliance
#
# Features:
# - FGDC and ISO 19115 standard compliance checking
# - Auto-generation of missing metadata fields
# - Batch validation for large datasets
# - Custom validation rules support
# - Export reports in XML, HTML, or PDF
#
# Supported Formats:
# - Shapefiles (.shp, .shx, .dbf, .prj)
# - GeoTIFF (.tif, .tiff)
# - GeoJSON (.geojson, .json)
# - KML/KMZ (.kml, .kmz)
# - PostGIS databases
#
# Usage:
# metadata-validator --input dataset.shp --standard fgdc --output report.xml
# metadata-validator --batch-validate directory/ --export-format html